title: BBS in a Box -- Classic Mac Collection 1992
description:
BBS IN A BOX Â¥ VOLUME VI
             Available  August 1, 1992


VOLUME VI Hits the Streets...

1.4 Gigabytes! 
There are many new items on Volume VI with a total of over 9,000 files and 640 megabytes of compressed Macintosh(tm) software. 

Decompressed this data exceeds 1.4 Gigabytes! This CD-ROM is the most current collection available with items added as late as June 20, 1992. Volume VI has expanded compatability to seven (7) BBS systems. First Class, Hermes, Mansion, MUBBS, Nova Link, Second Sight, and Telefinder. All of these BBS systems are excellent and we are trying to support as many sysops as possible. This disk is also a great tool for personal use!

Twenty-four software topics
Volume VI contains over 75 AppleLink items,  296 Adobe Screen font files, 100 MUG items,  323 Art files, 434 Business tools, 371 DA's,  407 Fonts, 531 Games,  1097 HyperCard tools, MacTechnical Notes, 372 MUG Newsletter Reviews, 117 MIDI files, 226 Music files, 393 Programer tools, 66 QuickTime tools, 575 Telecommunication files, 189 System7 tools, Decompression applications, 1000 utilities for the Macintosh, 240 Word processing tools and support articles plus much, much more!
